                                </p>
                                <div class="bg-slate-50 p-3 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 font-mono text-xs text-center text-slate-700 font-bold">
                                    z = (x - μ) / σ
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                `;
